--- Introduction

A program that builds translation memories

Part of http://www.softcatala.org/wiki/Mem%C3%B2ria_traducci%C3%B3_de_Softcatal%C3%A0 effort

--- Dependencies

* python-polib
*  transifex-client

--- Setting up

tx init --host https://fedora.transifex.net

tx set --auto-remote  https://fedora.transifex.net/projects/p/fedora/r/fedora-upstream-projects/
(account is username not e-mail)

tx pull -lca

--- Commands

Merging the translation memory with a new file

msgmerge -N tm.po new-pofile.po  > final-pofile.po

